object.text: (Remove this text before playing!) To place objects, copy them from the top left to your level, or manually change the class name of the object you just placed from the tilesets. Certain backgrounds (800x600 ones that don't repeat well vertically) require the level height to be set at 18 to look good. Make sure you put any tiles that aren't solid in Background or Foreground, or it will be solid! I will eventually work on making this not happen.
